quote>&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://holland.pk/j7osrh4g&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj7osrh4g%22&d=mDqfqm87OfudLvceUFIzAIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=649f36d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/j7osrh4g&quot;</a>  /&gt;<br />\n人地澳門狗啲 dc狗唔載港燦 好心唔好再去澳門旅遊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既鬼地方真係搵鬼去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n恭喜澳門將會繼奴隸國成為香港人第二個唔會去嘅地方。"},{"pid":"4999a40c522951c316e61ac56cc17195893b5806","tid":375022,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1472136323095774/permalink/1740775806231823/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1472136323095774%2Fpermalink%2F1740775806231823%2F&d=mDqfqm87OfudLvceUFIzAIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=939d4801\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1472136323095774/permalink/1740775806231823/</a><br />\n<br />\n成功收割光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1uza6qve\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1uza6qve&h=05096dca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e7d74e9e30141808eaaa59241d65fd3de0919c8","tid":375022,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://holland.pk/j7osrh4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj7osrh4g&d=mDqfqm87OfudLvceUFIzAIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8aac75f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/j7osrh4g</a>&quot;  /&gt;<br />\n人地澳門狗啲 dc狗唔載港燦 好心唔好再去澳門旅遊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既鬼地方真係搵鬼去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n恭喜澳門將會繼奴隸國成為香港人第二個唔會去嘅地方。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗下好啦，大把港豬仆住去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe9d383bc4af5eddac395a87e7017764e5b571f","tid":375022,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1472136323095774/permalink/1740775806231823/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1472136323095774%2Fpermalink%2F1740775806231823%2F&d=mDqfqm87OfudLvceUFIzAIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=939d4801\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1472136323095774/permalink/1740775806231823/</a><br />\n<br />\n成功收割光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1uza6qve\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1uza6qve&h=05096dca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地應該要全力支持共狗收返澳門<br />\n冇黨嘅帶領<br />\n佢一早超越香港唔知幾多倍<br />\n我好相信俾共慘黨收返之後一定可以超英趕美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42f7007a6385c4e67030f33efaa754cd94840ad","tid":375022,"uid":49508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話時話，支那都幾頭痕，對澳門拆關又唔係，唔拆又唔係。拆，賭場點算，廢左賭等於養多60萬廢人。支那侵略香港，搶奪香港資源，侵略澳門，仲要俾資源返澳門轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年中共唔肯要澳門係明智 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759f3a43f8475fc1de1e6011cafb0c128e95adfd","tid":375022,"uid":15603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"吹兩吹就淪陷係咪咁堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5e6b2e52730a3ce7f694ae95044ad9ac7c8cfe","tid":375022,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:56:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e56ed3c40b8990fbee1e67f2ca0bd7ecbbccf8cf","tid":375022,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:57:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吹兩吹就淪陷係咪咁堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比香港更成功嘅澳門<br />\n一個識善用一國兩制機遇嘅福地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人真係要好好習<br />\n<br />\n利：某張主席唔知咩時候講嘅說話"},{"pid":"7261f646a4f6d30136694147bb43be54686bad72","tid":375022,"uid":29804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搞唔掂咪搵中央幫手好正常 諗起迷你倉單野   唔掂又唔搵中央幫  消防都死埋  臉子真係咁重要咩？</blockquote><br />\n搵解放軍去死<br />\n中国啲消防廢到仆街"},{"pid":"9ca803de989aa4442578bc6096c6e114f5818991","tid":375022,"uid":24833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:01:33.000Z","msg":"條link 入面既留言先正，幾多人感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 澳狗幾撚時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c05d1aef4e4a38c46eb9892e76bf72b80ddad9","tid":375022,"uid":77453,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:01:55.000Z","msg":"其實澳門係別國內政，我國唔太應該說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor